ont-size:10px;color:#0000ff\">:</span><span style=\"font-size:10px;color:#a31515\">DataGrid</span><span style=\"font-size:10px;color:#0000ff\">&gt;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:10px\">But I get an error:<br>\r\nError 1 Value 'ContextMenu' cannot be assigned to property 'Property'. Invalid PropertyDescriptor value. E:\\WpfProjects\\BssExpeditor\\BssExpeditor\\Pages\\EmployeesPage.xaml 25 29 BssExpeditor<br>\r\n</span><br>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n",
